4. Karla Gendler

# Karla Gendra

## Research Engineering/Scientist Associate IV Project Management

Phone: **512-232-8106** |
Email: **[gendlerk@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:gendlerk@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Karla joined TACC in February, 2011. Previously she worked as a Scientific Analyst for CyVerse, and as a Senior Bioinformatics Scientist for ChromDB at the University of Arizona. Her responsibilities included supervising and providing technical direction to iPlant Genotype to Phenotype Project personnel in conjunction with Engagement Team Scientific Lead. She also helped define project scope, goals and deliverables in support of iPlant's goals in collaboration with senior management and project stakeholders. Karla has developed project plan documents and associated communications documents, as well as planned project timelines and tracks project milestones and deliverables using various project management tools.

### Education

**M.S., Applied Bioscience**  

University of Arizona

**B.S., Mathematics**  

Michigan State University